Class Quantum

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.basho.riak.client.core.query.timeseries.Quantum

  • public class Quantum
extends Object
    Holds the Quantum information for a Riak TimeSeries row. Used in conjunction with FullColumnDescription when receiving data from a DescribeTable command, or when creating a table with the CreateTable command.
